description: This is a market on who the upcoming HBO documentary will identify as Satoshi Nakamoto, the pseudonymous creator of Bitcoin.

markets.description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the HBO documentary" Money Electric: The Bitcoin Mystery" currently scheduled to air on October 8, identifies Paul Le Roux as the primary creator of Bitcoin. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No". 

If the documentary identifies multiple individuals, this market will resolve according to the individual which the documentary most directly depicts, or presents as most likely to be responsible for creating Bitcoin.

If Paul Le Roux and another individual(s) are presented as equally likely in the conclusion of the documentary, the market will resolve to "No".

If the documentary is not released by October 15, this market will resolve to "No".
markets.question: Will the HBO documentary identify Paul Le Roux as Satoshi?
